Weapon Enhancer/Armour Enhancer

--DONE--

- Added ghost shard scaling to weapons.


--NEXT--

- Add ghost shard scaling to NewShortsword and Sai onwards.


--NOTES--

- Ghost shard scaling affects perks of a weapon.

> Weapons with extra speed/accuracy get boosted speed/accuracy through ghosts shard but nerf damage bonus accordingly.
> Weapons with special abilities get larger values/smaller cooldowns for abilities from ghost shard bonus. Nerf damage accordingly.
> Balance around 4-5 ghost shards at end game for non-grinders. 


